.TH KERNEL-INSTALLER 1 "2026-01-24" "1.0.0" "Kernel Installer Manual"
.SH NAME
kernel-installer \- A graphical interface for downloading, compiling and installing the Linux kernel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kernel-installer
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B kernel-installer
is a GTK3 application designed to simplify the process of obtaining, configuring, and installing the Linux kernel. It supports multiple optimization profiles (Gaming, Audio/Video, Minimal) and is compatible with major Linux distributions.
.SH OPTIONS
This application does not take any command line options.
.SH KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
.TP
.B Ctrl+Q
Quit the application.
.TP
.B F5
Refresh available kernel versions.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /usr/share/kernel-installer/
Application data and logic.
.TP
.I ~/.kernel_installer_history.json
Installation history file.
